{"tid":1509002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立調查委員會已經有結果同建議！","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:42:41.000Z","uid":53683,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6d4773e59e765aef6587d890c23bde5cad0ebf","tid":1509002,"uid":53683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"林奠見所謂青年人個單嘢，有一樣嘢大家可能會忽略咗，<br />\n以下紅字證明咗根本港共政府即使成立獨立調查委員會，都只係會得出自己滿意既答案！<br />\n條柒婆未調查但已經可以預知調查結果同建議，<br />\n連登仔咁醒梗係唔會俾佢呃到，但要由呢一刻開始向淺黃同市民大眾宣傳！<br />\n我最驚有一日佢擺個獨立調查委員會出嚟就氹走咗一班人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭聽完11個青年分享後發言回應，稱要撤回《逃犯條例》修訂有難度，但沒有進一步闡䆁。至於獨立調查委員會，林鄭指很多人要求調查警察濫權，警隊對此很抗拒，要顧及有三萬人的警隊，不能貿然影響其工作，現時最重要是要停止暴力，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但林鄭稱英國曾有調查案例，有關調查結果和建議都很切合香港。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190826/59976495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F59976495&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a3a07876\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F59976495&h=51a927dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190826/59976495</a>"},{"pid":"5a524197340a72cc4b0a88ae99ab65477d55ec73","tid":1509002,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=e3798547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 